<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1>Blocitoff</h1>
  <p>Blocitoff is a self-destructing to-do list application!</p>
  <p>
      <%= link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> or 
      <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %> today!
  </p>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Create a to-do list</h2>
    <p>Blocitoff allows you to add as many items as you need to your list.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Keep your list up-to-date</h2>
    <p>Blocitoff lets you mark items as completed once you've accomplished a task.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <h2>Eliminate clutter</h2>
    <p>Blocitoff will automatically remove items after seven days to keep you focused on your most urgent tasks.</p>
  </div>
</div>